    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering 320hp through a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry that provides exceptional mechanical grip. Recent service includes a verified IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh clutch assembly, ensuring the integrity of the powertrain. Equipped with four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system offers consistent bite and minimal fade. This is a driver-focused example with a linear power curve and communicative hydraulic steering, ideal for those who value analog feedback and engineering purity.",
